{"tid":1273160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有文宣制定《廣場憲法》立會宣讀","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T18:16:50.000Z","uid":149630,"like":315,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1196596e5f36f4dc3fb12907edb1e9b3d9071c","tid":1273160,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳】召喚所有文宣制定《廣場憲法》立會宣讀<br />\n記你老母，不分化不割席不篤灰呢？又屌基本法又屌熱狗陳云，訓醒未？<br />\n<br />\n強調2大訴求：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、成立獨立調查會追究警方暴力<br />\n二、立刻實現基本法所承諾的立法會普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要1，2兩點到左手就點都得 所以唔好提第三點住 </span></span><br />\n因為會阻礙個進度模糊焦點 拉剧爆耐同犧牲更多先至有機會到手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">三、一次性特赦因社運而違法的集會人士，包括69 612 71 傘運魚革，例如梁天琦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長遠目標：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、普選特首<br />\n二、永續基本法，實現一國兩制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n設立死綫 i.e. 8：00 p.m. 等待政府回應，否則原地成立臨時政府並向外媒宣佈/刊登林鄭政府已不具合法性（legitimacy )，即時生效，並要求美國國會考慮通過《香港人權與民主法案》，實現聯邦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1272341/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1272341/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n根本唔應該以人廢言，為反而反，你如果唔同意唔該提出合理理據，唔係你同藍絲廢老有咩分別？所有嘅爭取必須要不違反中國領土主權同重大利益先有機會，你話你想獨立fine，咁你憑咩先？理想固然美好，嘴炮打天下，你想顛覆國家政權你咁勇嘅just go on ，你要自尋短見，冇人救到你。<br />\n<br />\n基本法係有保障一國兩制，同普選嘅權利，請明白你現在之所以有言論自由，集會自由，都係因爲有基本法。<br />\n<br />\n基本法就係有一國兩制，高度自治，問題唔係基本法到，係執行上面，只要有全面普選就可以自決前途<br />\n<br />\n2020普選立法會一定要列為要項，美國嘅香港人權與民主法案有列明呢一點，有美國助攻就能事半功倍<br />\nH.R.3289 - Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act of 2019:<br />\n&quot;(4) to support the establishment of a genuine democratic option to freely and fairly nominate and elect the Chief Executive of Hong Kong, and the establishment by 2020 of open and direct democratic elections for all members of the Hong Kong Legislative Council;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n後備方案<br />\n《方舟計劃》 香港2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1264945/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1264945/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1264944/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1264944/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n現需要各界精英加入<br />\n歡迎入谷討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=6589c115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w</a>"},{"pid":"f7988fcbf9e9f5361bd6a1cb4820fb596b489d55","tid":1273160,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"9ceb9abf1990f97561c5617fbf32032178a28bfe","tid":1273160,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14f10fd3637fc6ec994e39ed7f5e1e88071ec65f","tid":1273160,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c25e95bb5e2c6238dddcb996e187ca96343ab985","tid":1273160,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e77e98c92a4175715b62aaa5d1ec0aa4afa116e6","tid":1273160,"uid":187647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"600ec46883e662a4d58810d8ec451d5807884b7a","tid":1273160,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229bc89e262af009d4f54770e7325f00366dc8e9","tid":1273160,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"3b7886fd19551eed9eb381690b6eef7818c4ed46","tid":1273160,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0