09873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1926af311b922cb4a001b24433ef5e3923177dc7","tid":1273160,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"行動同訴求一致<br />\n<br />\n咁就出師有名<br />\n<br />\n普選立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb4247563c22e0598a2cc50c68720f3551c420d","tid":1273160,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fb79ed14798b7dca86d98eb01cf2582417b21dc","tid":1273160,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"今日， 一大群香港市民衝入立法會議廳，係因為議會已經無法代表人民的聲音。1984年，中國政府簽署中英聯合聲明，向香港人承諾1997年7月1日後，港人治港，高度自治，開放政治選舉制度，全面普選議會及香港特區首長。然而，中國政府食言自肥，肆意操弄選舉制度，製造出票值不等的無認受性議會，不斷施延自治區政府首長的選舉及扭曲民主普選的普世價值和打壓爭取民主選舉的社運人士。香港人現在必須蒴本清源，解散現時缺乏記受性的全體立法會，以普選方式重新選出新一屆立法機關，廢除功能組別及分組點票制度。特赦所有參與社會公民運動的政治檢控罪犯。<br />\n<br />\n(轉發)"},{"pid":"fe8ca31b65b804eb54a54167709b5ec00511f031","tid":1273160,"uid":147880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d7327ab77d1f8a8f73822702168060c94b864c88","tid":1273160,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"頂 我miss左admin個message<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc81da4c91e8f69a38236ace295a832233374580","tid":1273160,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf8e8468034047907e8a27c7b5379467a2c4041d","tid":1273160,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ee7b0dc49b71b3dd26b4cdbfedec81e43ece006","tid":1273160,"uid":250580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score